{"tid":133662,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣同内向嘅男仔相處好","createTime":"2017-02-24T19:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T16:32:40.000Z","uid":87467,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce11c186ce415ff71694d51825613418aca9b88","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:11:02.000Z","msg":"依加已經曖昧左一個半月<br />\n有出過街食飯睇戲<br />\n但最多都淨係試過拉住佢書包帶炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想佢可以同我表白同拖手<br />\n求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef9ba5fd217ce6e63e6ac88742631e24ac16202","tid":133662,"uid":15906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:12:33.000Z","msg":"你同佢表白唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你講到佢咁內向 咪你主動"},{"pid":"0ef52f815731bf720b29b0207709523722939d87","tid":133662,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:12:38.000Z","msg":"我同個女仔拉鋸左3個月左右，最近終於主動拖左佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fef2d772e95966c19b722bb2ca1d60a3429d52","tid":133662,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:12:45.000Z","msg":"唔好逼佢講野 一定會反感<br />\n<br />\n唔好逼人告白 要告自己主動"},{"pid":"0000cca5d18fab260f2421fdd5fa77f27f163494","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你同佢表白唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你講到佢咁內向 咪你主動</blockquote><br />\n佢前女友都係掂一掂手就當一齊<br />\n我又唔想咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7b751f26fae56a3f71120beaab5b66e602586d","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同個女仔拉鋸左3個月左右，最近終於主動拖左佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曖昧咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會好快唔中意"},{"pid":"6b6fb786e93cebe7c61f7ce4857d94a405c80fab","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好逼佢講野 一定會反感<br />\n<br />\n唔好逼人告白 要告自己主動</blockquote><br />\n我又驚會唔會嚇親佢 話曬佢真係勁慢熱"},{"pid":"9bcd4a5fed197f235790392298009aaddbcf6363","tid":133662,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我同個女仔拉鋸左3個月左右，最近終於主動拖左佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曖昧咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會好快唔中意</blockquote><br />\n唔會掛，我開頭都以為曖昧咁耐感覺會遞減。但係當大家都開始了解對方既時候，感覺反而不斷上升，我拖到手，攬下都滿足~~不過始終要男仔踏出第一步先。"},{"pid":"6efb026882b91a6d81e0e30aa3889914ec5e64d6","tid":133662,"uid":82747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:24:58.000Z","msg":"壁咚"},{"pid":"cf7ea7d64b6c2d4a1819f2697e8a963c77a7451c","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>壁咚</blockquote><br />\n難啲 佢高大過我咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40602cde2ed3b190264ac3c719e8e8aa0df017a","tid":133662,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:27:00.000Z","msg":"我考慮左好耐先踏出第一步(驚我諗多左，驚食檸檬，驚冇女朋友既同時，又冇左個好朋友)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c950737cb3eb3e299c3e6aa742a2c32931609e4","tid":133662,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我同個女仔拉鋸左3個月左右，最近終於主動拖左佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曖昧咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會好快唔中意</blockquote><br />\n唔會掛，我開頭都以為曖昧咁耐感覺會遞減。但係當大家都開始了解對方既時候，感覺反而不斷上升，我拖到手，攬下都滿足~~不過始終要男仔踏出第一步先。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你暖昧未必直接對於鍾意你 要告白<br />\n有時係想認識你更多 再仔細考量<br />\n呢個時候女方太急好容易失敗"},{"pid":"2093d2774aa45825254476c4140db0254fae1145","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我同個女仔拉鋸左3個月左右，最近終於主動拖左佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曖昧咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會好快唔中意</blockquote><br />\n唔會掛，我開頭都以為曖昧咁耐感覺會遞減。但係當大家都開始了解對方既時候，感覺反而不斷上升，我拖到手，攬下都滿足~~不過始終要男仔踏出第一步先。</blockquote><br />\n同佢行街 隻手都唔知放邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次搭地鐵好逼 我要捉住佢手臂先企得穩<br />\n勁想佢主動拖我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7a2ccbd3c6d2cc6fee528f7f0ee435b510bac8","tid":133662,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:31:28.000Z","msg":"拎支hand cream出嚟，唔小心一嘢擠多咗<br />\n跟住講：哎也唔小心擠多咗，伸隻手出嚟啦<br />\n慢慢hi落佢隻手度(進取d就幫佢搽埋)<br />\n然後笑住講：heehee唔好嘥~"},{"pid":"0f5579148a52f6c9a7672e40aad3c40038d6bef9","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:32:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我同個女仔拉鋸左3個月左右，最近終於主動拖左佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曖昧咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會好快唔中意</blockquote><br />\n唔會掛，我開頭都以為曖昧咁耐感覺會遞減。但係當大家都開始了解對方既時候，感覺反而不斷上升，我拖到手，攬下都滿足~~不過始終要男仔踏出第一步先。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你暖昧未必直接對於鍾意你 要告白<br />\n有時係想認識你更多 再仔細考量<br />\n呢個時候女方太急好容易失敗</blockquote><br />\n我都知 再加上佢前幾個月先同女朋友散<br />\n我膽粗粗問佢係咪只係覺得我性格好 先會對我咁好<br />\n佢話係我係佢低潮個時拉佢一把<br />\n<br />\n下意識勁想反問佢 咁你對我咁好係咪淨係想報恩<br />\n但又問唔出口<br />\n我就笑笑口話無嘢啦 我都唔知我想點<br />\n佢反而話 我知自己想點喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c394be23ef4e63f22ce6b8269eb0685b7353938d","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:33:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我考慮左好耐先踏出第一步(驚我諗多左，驚食檸檬，驚冇女朋友既同時，又冇左個好朋友)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好幸福吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cdd5311de16637207cbb2c5e5d449ec299ca21","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎支hand cream出嚟，唔小心一嘢擠多咗<br />\n跟住講：哎也唔小心擠多咗，伸隻手出嚟啦<br />\n慢慢hi落佢隻手度(進取d就幫佢搽埋)<br />\n然後笑住講：heehee唔好嘥~</blockquote><br />\n係咪成功例子來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a9e8806a1b05a9dc8fcb9ed3be414e44bb4eaf","tid":133662,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:34:36.000Z","msg":"直接同佢講"},{"pid":"1abbe13bc4ddec89ddf93f5c85374fe263858f01","tid":133662,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拎支hand cream出嚟，唔小心一嘢擠多咗<br />\n跟住講：哎也唔小心擠多咗，伸隻手出嚟啦<br />\n慢慢hi落佢隻手度(進取d就幫佢搽埋)<br />\n然後笑住講：heehee唔好嘥~</blockquote><br />\n係咪成功例子來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吓，你唔係諗住咩都唔做唔引下佢先走去表白嘛？<br />\n男人呢d俾多d空間佢幻想下就得"},{"pid":"a22b0984954b509c9110065cc17c83469170c226","tid":133662,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我同個女仔拉鋸左3個月左右，最近終於主動拖左佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曖昧咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會好快唔中意</blockquote><br />\n唔會掛，我開頭都以為曖昧咁耐感覺會遞減。但係當大家都開始了解對方既時候，感覺反而不斷上升，我拖到手，攬下都滿足~~不過始終要男仔踏出第一步先。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你暖昧未必直接對於鍾意你 要告白<br />\n有時係想認識你更多 再仔細考量<br />\n呢個時候女方太急好容易失敗</blockquote><br />\n我都知 再加上佢前幾個月先同女朋友散<br />\n我膽粗粗問佢係咪只係覺得我性格好 先會對我咁好<br />\n佢話係我係佢低潮個時拉佢一把<br />\n<br />\n下意識勁想反問佢 咁你對我咁好係咪淨係想報恩<br />\n但又問唔出口<br />\n我就笑笑口話無嘢啦 我都唔知我想點<br />\n佢反而話 我知自己想點喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你想俾佢知你鍾意佢<br />\n至少你要俾佢覺得 你對佢冇戒心<br />\n你報恩個句 已經俾佢覺得你懷疑佢非真心"},{"pid":"cc1e0556947f82ceece69e9fffd6cc9d8103adb0","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我同個女仔拉鋸左3個月左右，最近終於主動拖左佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曖昧咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會好快唔中意</blockquote><br />\n唔會掛，我開頭都以為曖昧咁耐感覺會遞減。但係當大家都開始了解對方既時候，感覺反而不斷上升，我拖到手，攬下都滿足~~不過始終要男仔踏出第一步先。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你暖昧未必直接對於鍾意你 要告白<br />\n有時係想認識你更多 再仔細考量<br />\n呢個時候女方太急好容易失敗</blockquote><br />\n我都知 再加上佢前幾個月先同女朋友散<br />\n我膽粗粗問佢係咪只係覺得我性格好 先會對我咁好<br />\n佢話係我係佢低潮個時拉佢一把<br />\n<br />\n下意識勁想反問佢 咁你對我咁好係咪淨係想報恩<br />\n但又問唔出口<br />\n我就笑笑口話無嘢啦 我都唔知我想點<br />\n佢反而話 我知自己想點喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你想俾佢知你鍾意佢<br />\n至少你要俾佢覺得 你對佢冇戒心<br />\n你報恩個句 已經俾佢覺得你懷疑佢非真心</blockquote><br />\n好彩無講出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c0237e885d0a725e7ce75591e39dc9e4c5e690","tid":133662,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:42:00.000Z","msg":"同佢講我隻手好凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6995a77491bde4456238be5f0233d18fa539bc89","tid":133662,"uid":67837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:42:32.000Z","msg":"可以行路/過馬路抆下手袖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6863ad56230e6a51d5697850cac3bc7515cd75","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以行路/過馬路抆下手袖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾好喎！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088105538661be8330b8bee45eca3b76590ddc53","tid":133662,"uid":87467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢講我隻手好凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個心仲凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}